(Applicable to New Business/ Retention and Call Type)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    How to claim (what You must do)
You must tell Us within 30 days if You know about any
event that will, or is likely to result in a claim. As soon
as possible after telling Us, You must give Us:
• details about any other insurance covering the same event;
• details of the event;
• any proof, document, information or sworn statement We ask for;
• documents or details of communications You receive about a claim; and
• any assistance. We may require to obtain settlement from any other party.
